name: Santa's little helper - Rainbow child
description:
1 cute little wombat making a heck of a mess "helping" with wrapping up presents for the big day and loving every minute. Gift wrapping ribbons in marbled red, purple and yellow - too much colour or just enough Rainbow child?  Maybe some other colours suit your style better? 

Size - approximately 11cm square png, 300ppi
